headline: Xylem (XYL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Xylem trades at $143 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 10.2% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 10.5%.
